title: Deportivo Warnes
text:
Deortivo Warnes is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club from <a href="Santa%20Cruz%20de%20la%20Sierra">Santa Cruz</a>, <a href="Bolivia">Bolivia</a> currently playing at Santa Cruz Primera A.
The club was founded September 23, 1996 by Brazilian Engineers, and they play their home games at the <a href="Estadio%20Samuel%20Vaca%20Jimenez">Estadio Samuel Vaca Jimenez</a>.
